<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="clear-adj">clear <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /klɪə(r)/    美 /klɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-transparent">1.★ <strong>清澈的；透明的(transparent)；晴朗的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the clear water of a lake
清澈的湖水</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>clear glass
透明的玻璃</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a clear sky / day
晴空/晴天</p></div>

<h4 id="2-plain">2.★ <strong>清楚的；明显的；明确的(plain)：</strong></h4>
<p>反 unclear </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a clear photograph / voice
清晰的照片/声音</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a clear advantage in the contest
在比赛中有明显的优势</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a clear purpose / goal
有明确的目标</p><footer>2009 江苏</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ladies and gentlemen, have I <strong>made myself clear</strong>?
女士们、先生们，我讲清楚了吗？</p><footer>2009 湖北书面表达改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>be clear about / on:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you’re clear about where you want to go, the rest of the world will either help you get there or get out of the way. 
如果你清楚自己想去哪儿，世界上其余的一切都会帮你到达那里或为你让路。</p><footer>2014 全国</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>it is clear + (that) / wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is clear that your life in your country is quite different from mine.
很显然，你们国家的生活方式与我的大不相同。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was not clear why the man hadn’t reported the accident sooner.
人们尚不清楚那个人为什么没有早一点报告这起事故。</p><footer>2011 江苏</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>无障碍的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a clear view / road 
一览无余/畅通的道路</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>(头脑) 清醒的；（思路）清晰的：：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>keep a clear head / mind
保持清醒的头脑</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>clearly /ˈklɪəli/ adv   </p></div>